{"tid":2424133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★「基金教父」：資金移至舊經濟，投資者重新審視科技的投資價值！","createTime":"2021-02-26T10:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T10:50:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4d249fd2ce503b298a96302354ee05c1f9893d87","tid":2424133,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:32:55.000Z","msg":"「基金教父」雷賢達表示，債息上升對高估值的新經濟股影響較大，相信資金由新經濟股轉移至舊經濟股的趨勢會持續。他指出，美國10年期國債孳息率由去年初近2厘回落至0.5厘水平，科技股估值獲得重估而表現強勢，到債息近日重上1.5厘，亦會令投資者重新審視科技股的投資價值，料<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>科技股今年難以再跑贏</strong></span>可受惠未來經濟復甦的舊經濟股。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210226/bkn-20210226092516738-0226_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20210226%2Fbkn-20210226092516738-0226_00842_001.html&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B5E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=662da5e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210226/bkn-20210226092516738-0226_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a2a66b4f1b2fa5659a3ae8bf5b2466eb0b100a5d","tid":2424133,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:33:14.000Z","msg":"World No IT confirmed<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148b5703dce62d40dfdb39b0848c0fdf9ee0a1d6","tid":2424133,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f6a508122629535500f55f152db19812f8a04c","tid":2424133,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0